{"tid":2355121,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"與老公Kanye West再傳婚變！Kim已搵定離婚律師","createTime":"2021-01-06T02:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T02:53:39.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4fa16f49543b62915b5f80ffc1a2194abab4a9","tid":2355121,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210106/photo/bkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001_01p.jpg?20210106101249\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20210106101249&h=6bb811c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國真人騷女王Kim Kardashian與樂壇天王老公Kanye West婚變的消息近期不絕於耳，美國報章《紐約郵報》昨日就以頭版爆他們即將離婚！<br />\n<br />\n據知她已聘請專打離婚官司的名律師Laura Wasser為她打離婚官司。之前Kim與第2任老公NBA球星堪富利斯（Kris Humphries）離婚時亦是由她協助打離婚官司。消息人士說：「佢哋將離婚保持低調但佢哋已經玩完。而雙方已傾緊離婚協議。」另有消息指他們仍就物業分配一事未達成共識。<br />\n<br />\n查實她們近期已有婚變的迹象，她近期被見到沒有戴住婚戒之餘，在過去的聖誕以及新年都未見Kanye陪伴她度過，她只與母親Kris Jenner、姊妹和子女一同出埠慶祝。至於Kanye就留在懷俄明的牧場大宅。據知她唔想老公與她過節等她們靜靜地處理分居與離婚的事情。而他去年7月已在社交網站自爆曾嘗試與老婆搞離婚，他當時指自從Kim於18年11月與饒舌男歌手Meek Mill一同出席有關爭取監獄改革的論壇後已想與她離婚。當時他亦稱呼外母Kris Jenner為「Kris正恩」，並爆她們一家嘗試迫他接受心理治療。Kim與Kanye暫時未就離婚傳聞作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210106/photo/bkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001_02p.jpg?20210106101249\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20210106101249&h=33a6b8e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e884e0502c2cd85c6fd579bb4224b56ce932706","tid":2355121,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210106/mobile/bkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001.html&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=2a151c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210106/mobile/bkn-20210106093157275-0106_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"658ebae8176e919287dc6f260b2d4f00da359327","tid":2355121,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"bound 2"},{"pid":"8888727f9d4a1e297979321d75e0794a7f3f09d3","tid":2355121,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"事但啦<br />\n反正佢兩個都怪人黎"}]}